  "detailed_description": "This is the official digital adaptation of the MagnyTour board game.<br><br>You'll take the role of a team manager and guide your team of 3 runners trough a series of grueling races that wind their way through mountains, plains and time trials.<br><br>In this turn-based game, every action must be carefully considered for each of your three specialized racers (climber, sprinter, and all-rounder):<br><br><strong>    => Roll the dice to set your pace and risk encountering technical problems</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/963f2726b0b1ac91db4b8afd9d92fc12.poster.avif?t=1742754952\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/963f2726b0b1ac91db4b8afd9d92fc12.webm?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/963f2726b0b1ac91db4b8afd9d92fc12.mp4?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>    => Take advantage of the slipstream created by other racers to follow them</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/2cbfc94a84e64737ae6053f41c80d5c1.poster.avif?t=1742754952\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/2cbfc94a84e64737ae6053f41c80d5c1.webm?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/2cbfc94a84e64737ae6053f41c80d5c1.mp4?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>    => Strategically wait to slow down the racers behind you and create a gap</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/19b903b28a0eba9058ee1a2ee56cf153.poster.avif?t=1742754952\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/19b903b28a0eba9058ee1a2ee56cf153.webm?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/19b903b28a0eba9058ee1a2ee56cf153.mp4?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>    => Seize an opportunity to attack and break away from the peloton</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/bd9b5b1a89beaa3d96bc95a16c1287b4.poster.avif?t=1742754952\" width=480 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/bd9b5b1a89beaa3d96bc95a16c1287b4.webm?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1971570/extras/bd9b5b1a89beaa3d96bc95a16c1287b4.mp4?t=1742754952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>The game offers several options for guiding your racers, and each racer has their own strengths and weaknesses. As a manager, you will need to take these differences into account and choose your strategy accordingly.<br>MagnyTour offers a strategy and tactics-rich gaming experience for fans of cycling and simulation games.<br><br>Features:<br><br>* Choose between \"classic\" one-day race, Tour or time trial<br>* Solo mode against AI<br>* Online multiplayer mode with up-to 6 players",
